    Get Start

    Enrich the enriched result (enrich^2)

    First enrich genes by clusterProfiler…

    ego <- enrichGO(gene          = gene,
                  universe      = names(geneList),
                  OrgDb         = org.Hs.eg.db,
                  ont           = "BP",
                  pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                  pvalueCutoff  = 0.5,
                  qvalueCutoff  = 0.5,
                  readable      = TRUE)

    Then, run obj |> EnrichGT() !

    obj <- ego |> EnrichGT()
